OOC, I thought you'd enjoy that post Robo.

BIC, Foxfingers backed further away, he was satisfied with the reaction he'd
recieved and decided that it was time to take another chance. slowly he
lowered the vial to his side remaining prepared to use it at a moments
notice. "It would seem that we're at a stand still. You have your army and I
have this." he tilted his head slightly indicateing the vial that was
keeping him from being dismantled alive.  He nodded toward Kit Kat2, "You at
one point gave me the benefit of the doubt even though you saw I was wearing
a Maximal symbol." remembering back he remembered that she also tried to
slip a tracking devise on him but he had alterior matives as well which in
his mind made them even. (Events courtesy of past events in the packs old
base.)  he'd caught the female wolfs scent in the corridor and sensed
something different about it. (It is after all a clone.) "I was forced to
break into your base to avoid being char broiled when you submerged. I
wasn't aware that this was your base or I would've tried more diplomatic
channels to get Silver Scout back." he wanted to tell the whole truth but
this didn't seem to be the time. "What can I do to get out of this mess in
one piece?" He asked predicting thier answer, "Other than give you this vial
that is."
